{"word":"H1104 - בָּלַע - bâlaʻ - baw-lah' - Cover","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בָּלַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bâlaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>baw-lah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Cover"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விழுங்கு. அவ மதி, விழுங்கிப்போடு, அழி அகற்ற மூடு, நிர்மூலமாக்கு,முழுகிப்போ, நாசமடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to swallow down, to swallow up, to engulf, to eat up"},{"paragraph":"a (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to swallow down"},{"paragraph":"2) to swallow up, to engulf"},{"paragraph":"b (Niphal) to be swallowed up"},{"paragraph":"c (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to swallow"},{"paragraph":"2) to swallow up, to engulf"},{"paragraph":"3) squandering (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"d) (Pual) to be swallowed up"},{"paragraph":"e) (Hithpael) to be ended"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>make away with</i> (specifically by <i>swallowing</i>); generally to <i>destroy: - </i>cover, destroy, devour, eat up, be at end, spend up, swallow down (up)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1104 - בָּלַע - bâlaʻ - baw-lah'/1104\">H1104</a>, <a href=\"#/H1105 - בֶּלַע - belaʻ - beh'-lah/1105\">H1105</a>, <a href=\"#/H1106 - בֶּלַע - Belaʻ - beh'-lah/1106\">H1106</a>, <a href=\"#/H1108 - בַּלְעִי - Balʻîy - bel-ee'/1108\">H1108</a>, <a href=\"#/H1109 - בִּלְעָם - Bilʻâm - bil-awm'/1109\">H1109</a>"}]}